{"tid":2083172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.28 靜默遊行回顧 by. SUCK Channel","createTime":"2020-06-28T14:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:00:56.000Z","uid":282534,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0b366954a705b608a0eb60cf167d6e39b1cb5215","tid":2083172,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"回顧今日重點<br />\n<br />\n首先感謝大家今日係7.1前既高風險日子依家願意上街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢份勇氣 唔係好多人都擁有 <br />\n而且大部份人今日都識避開防線轉入內街繼嫌行<br />\n呢份be water既靈活運用亦值得一贊<br />\n<br />\n今日有出黎既大家可以自傲一下<br />\n<br />\n然後到小細節&quot;反思&quot;<br />\n<br />\n今日其實有好多中年人都有份幫手出黎<br />\n但好像<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔係好多人都知個主題係 &quot;靜默遊行&quot; </span></span></strong><br />\n以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> &quot;靜&quot; </span></strong>作為主題<br />\n希望大家下次可以提提身邊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地多次強調今次一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> &quot;靜&quot; </span></strong>既原因<br />\n就係因為要令到大家既<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">行事低調迷彩化</span><br />\n呢樣野係可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">極大地&quot;保障大家既安全&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n先唔講到<span style=\"color: orange;\">主題性不太符合</span><br />\n其次就係如果咁做就係等於你係街大叫<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;我依家係黎示威 , 你黎拉走我啦&quot;</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且仲會令到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同行身邊幾米既人一齊提高左風險</span></strong>俾人圍起SS  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要佢有小小唔妥你就拉走你<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲會發起 &quot;靜默式&quot; 行動</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且仲會<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開發其他 &quot;新行動&quot;</span></strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家下次可以教教身邊既人或者其他走得比較慢既同行者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由7月起  攻守轉換 ❗️ <br />\n我地要重奪返抗爭行動模式既主導權 ❗️<br />\n由被動既一方轉成主動出擊既一方 ❗️</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後各位7.1見</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83e939313b0632f713a4d7b434bcf88c64d86ce","tid":2083172,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1f3008106827d40349431832dd3991e726dab7","tid":2083172,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"仲有如果可以既話  就盡量推廣 telegram 使用普及率<br />\n<br />\n因為telegram真係會有好多即時既抗爭資訊"},{"pid":"25752442990a1ad59c00221009aa95bf456a3107","tid":2083172,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"記得<br />\n要<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">靜</div>"},{"pid":"fa213298f496f64a354ec4814300d12e0be791f2","tid":2083172,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"今次係一個好突別o既嘗試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記得唔好密密玩, 否則會玩爛"},{"pid":"b232fe381eb6b08c0f68176adabbd997a31677af","tid":2083172,"uid":109345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"新技能解鎖<br />\n多謝suck"},{"pid":"0f1094cdbc6df61f23fe53e49e40e60ad99f9384","tid":2083172,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\